headline: Equinix (EQIX) Q4 FFO and Revenues Miss Estimates
summary: Equinix (EQIX) delivered FFO and revenue surprises of -2.10% and 0.79%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
